title: DLSA Jayashankar Bhupalpally Recruitment 2025 - Apply Offline for Chief Legal Aid Defense Counsel Posts
description: The District Legal Services Authority Jayashankar Bhupalpally (DLSAJayashankar Bhupalpally) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 01 Chief Legal Aid Defense Counsel Jobs. Interested and eligible candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their Any Degree, LLB can apply for the DLSA Jayashankar Bhupalpally Recruitment 2025 . The interested applicants can apply in offline mode. Here ...
